{"tid":2136963,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"有蘋果供應商 將六條生產線由中國搬去印度 產值達50億美元 影響55,000職位","createTime":"2020-08-02T13:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T01:58:50.000Z","uid":48083,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0bb1268c4799ef33026172d1040f76e1fae7cc04","tid":2136963,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T13:54:46.000Z","msg":"Apple vendor eyes production shift to India<br />\nSidhartha <br />\n<br />\nNEW DELHI: In a major relocation from China as part of global business&rsquo; effort for derisking of manufacturing bases by diversifying supply chains, a contract manufacturer for Apple is shifting six production lines looking forward to exporting around $5 billion worth of iPhones from India apart from catering to the domestic market. <br />\n<br />\nThe establishment of the facility is expected to generate employment for around 55,000 Indian workers over a year or so, sources familiar with the exercise told TOI. The vendors may expand the operations beyond phones to include tablets and even computers and laptops in the coming years. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.timesofindia.com/business/india-business/apple-vendor-eyes-production-shift-to-india/articleshow/77309542.cms\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fapple-vendor-eyes-production-shift-to-india%2Farticleshow%2F77309542.cms&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAneQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=08f5e4ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.timesofindia.com/business/india-business/apple-vendor-eyes-production-shift-to-india/articleshow/77309542.cms</a>"},{"pid":"60035c26e1e194f0bd20c5d6c4770e04b3764437","tid":2136963,"uid":33874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T13:56:19.000Z","msg":"屌呀<br />\n咁強國仲點抄"},{"pid":"90da566fa5c968506ad30ad48d972d5563eb9694","tid":2136963,"uid":289946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T14:03:12.000Z","msg":"下崗